  "description": [
    "THE BENGAL HURKARU the press is now free for which I among thousands pray a SHIPPING IN TELLIGENCE long and happy old age to Him who made it so and whose name I revere so much that it shall not appear herethis CALCUTTA JUNE S being the case 1 take leave to inform the Doctor that I shall always at my own hazard have a fling at whatevei ARRIVALSThe English ship Margaret Ain Capt J P Philipps from Bombay 14th May strikes my reason as ridiculous And should T have occa Passengers per Margaret Aun from Bombay in terms which he condescends to imagine were meant for verse I disclaim having made any attack at all upon Doc tor Tytler in the hints which displeased him so much Zoi hus Sciomachy is an imaginary person who in his positive way endeavours to account for certain phenomena and if Doe tor R Tytler insists upog identifying himself with this shadowy thingit is no fault of mine He has indeed bounced up toa peg spon which suspended a certain cap and without asking my leave he has clapped it upon his own head I would ask the Doctor if it was courteous"
